data.description:
For all the hard work you do, you deserve this!!! This open floor plan is perfect for entertaining. The formal dining room with a high ceiling and crown molding is just right for those candlelight diners. The living room has a centrally located fireplace, and lots of windows to watch the kids play out back from the comfort of your couch. The chef in the family will love the kitchen with granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, breakfast bar for extra seating. The open kitchen is great for cooking and entertaining at the same time. When it is time to escape to the master bedroom at the day's end, privacy and comfort are what you get. Plenty of room for your king or queen-bedroom furniture with room left for a reading or desk area. The master bath will take your breath away with a separate shower, and a huge walk-in closet that can be used as a dressing area. When you get tired of being inside you can go out back and enjoy the large covered patio while you watch the kids and the dogs run and play in the large backyard. See for yourself the family features this home offers.  This home is in a Golf Course community, the Club House is just a few minutes walk from the house.  Call today for an appointment.
The seller will provide $10,000 in concession, to use for buydown and closing costs.
